channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-21281] Repl checkpointing doesn't work when retry bootstrap load with partitions of external tables.
item.description: Repl checkpoint feature optimises the retry logic of bootstrap repl load by skipping the properly loaded tables and partitions. In case of retry of bootstrap load with external tables having partitions, the checkpoint doesn't work and load partitions always.
item.summary: Repl checkpointing doesn't work when retry bootstrap load with partitions of external tables.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
